Recommends: rtl-sdr
Description: Vintage military-style FM radio application for RTL-SDR
 Vintage Tactical Radio is a native Linux application that provides a
 vintage military/tactical radio interface for RTL-SDR v3 hardware.
 It features:
  - AM/FM broadcast reception (530 kHz - 1.7 GHz)
  - Military-inspired vintage UI with multiple themes
  - 7-band parametric equalizer with presets
  - 100 memory channels
  - Direct sampling for HF bands
  - Support for active antennas with bias-T
